  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the incidence of tachy- and bradyarrhythmic episodes
      in patients with acute myocardial infarction with depressed ventricular function and to
      determine the predictive value of several invasive and non-invasive risk markers for
      life-threatening arrhythmia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
